I am writing in reference to your recent call to our technical support center regarding the issue with the replacement of the tips.

Could you please provide a phone number where I can contact you? I would like to discuss the issue with you via phone call.

Additionally, I would like to confirm a suitable time frame for the call. This will allow us to review the issue and complete the necessary steps for the replacement process. We will also need some photos for reference.

Please let me know your availability so we can schedule a convenient time for the call.
